	"[\"text\"] = \"Feanor created the Silmarils using a crystal substance named silima.  They contain some of the light from the two great trees of Valinor (made by Yavanna and Nienna) named Telperion the Silver and Laurelin the Gold.  They are among the most prized of all the wonders crafted by the Elves.\\\n\\\n" ..
	"Both Silmarils contain the power of two of the Mystic Rods.  Both require a silima base combined with some of the essence from one tree.  Both items must then be fused together in a dual furnace.\\\n\\\n" ..
	"\\\n\\\nSILVER SILMARIL OF TELPERION\\\n\\\n" ..
	"Contains the most powerful transformation, allowing flight and extremely fast travel.  A secondary function allows you to summon, call, and dismiss a deadly minion.  Right click a guardian to customize it's behavior. All guardians attack evil monsters on sight, such as the spiders of Mirkwood.\\\n\\\n" ..
	"\\\n\\\nGOLD SILMARIL OF LAURELIN\\\n\\\n" ..
	"Heals yourself and any players in a medium-range beam.  Heals for more than the Rod of Healing.  A secondary function blinds and paralyzes players, and does an even more massive amount of damage to monsters than the Rod of Doom.\\\n\\\n\"}"
